</b></p>
<p>354. JUA 22/08/2014. Case no: THA 9/2014. State reply: None. Alleged arbitrary arrest, 
</p>
<p>detention, ill-treatment and torture in custody of a student activist by members of the 
</p>
<p>military forces. 
</p>
<p>355. JAL 01/07/2014. Case no: THA 5/2014. State reply: 09/09/2014. Allegations of 
</p>
